NEW DELHI, March 15 (Xinhua) -- The Indian Council of
Agricultural Research (ICAR) has prepared a "national agricultural
technology project" to ensure a sustainable and equitable
development in the agricultural sector, Agriculture Minister
Chaturanan Mishra said here today.
