<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, March 15 (Xinhua) -- Thailand will share its expertise
in breeding freshwater fish to help develop fishery and
aquaculture in the Mekong River countries of Laos, Cambodia and
Myanmar, a report said today.
</P>
<P>
