tournament after the early departures of world number-one Pete
Sampras, Goran Ivanisevic, Thomas Enqvist, Jim Courier and Agassi.
</P>
<P>
Unseeded Swede Jonas Bjorkman, ranked 35th in the world,
polished off the last seeded player left in the top half of the
draw on Friday with a 6-2, 6-3 win over number 14 Alberto
Berasategui of Spain.
</P>
