citizens from Tirana is under way, according to the ANA's
correspondent in the Albanian capital. Italian Chinook helicopters
have been in the Tirana football field to pick up evacuees.
</P>
<P>
According to the report, Tirana is quieter today than Thursday,
although sporadic gunfire is still being heard and the atmosphere
is tense. 
