<HEADLINE> Netherlands to Aid Tanzania's Rural Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, March 14 (Xinhua) -- The Netherlands will
provide 72.5 million U.S. Dollars to Tanzania between 1997 and
2003 under agreements on the Tanzanian-Netherlandish District
Rural Development Program signed here today.
</P>
<P>
Tanzania's Principal Secretary in the Ministry of Finance
Peter Ngumbullu and Netherlands's Ambassador to Tanzania Ajoerd
Leonstra signed the agreements on behalf of their respective
governments.
</P>
<P>
