agricultural extension, land-use planning, village demarcation,
road improvement, health care and water supply, said the
statement.
</P>
<P>
"For the present phase, the main vision and direction of the
approach, the management set-up and the mode of implementation
have been brought in line with the national reform programs,"
said the statement. enditem

