<HEADLINE> Nigeria Needs One Billion U.S. Dollars for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, March 14 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria needs 88 billion Naira
(about one billion U.S. Dollars) of investment to meet the
current demand for telecommunications services, the News Agency
of Nigeria reported today.
</P>
<P>
