from the Albanian government and his mission was to get them to
cooperate with each other to reestablish some sense of control and
security in the Balkan country.
</P>
<P>
Albright told reporters that the U.S. task force has evacuated
some 500 Americans out of Albania. But the evacuation has been
suspended temporarily for security reasons, but it will continue.
</P>
<P>
It was reported that the U.S. Marine helicopters were taking
ground fire in two incidents without any injury or damage. 
